<title type="html"><![CDATA[9/10 (Thu.) How to prolong our health span? / What steals my time? (Host: Lawrence)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=426&amp;p=444#p444"><![CDATA[
<span style="color: #FF0000">Thursday gathering of Royal Club is relocated to Ikari 怡客咖啡, 台北市衡陽路116號</span><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Session 1. How to prolong our health span?</span><br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.yogamotion.com/10-steps-to-increase-your-health-span/">https://www.yogamotion.com/10-steps-to- ... alth-span/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1, What do you think of the tips suggested in this article?<br />2, What do you think you should do or change so that you can be more healthy?<br />3, Do you think people in Taiwan is living longer, also healthy? Do you think our National Insurance can help us to live long and healthy lives?<br />4, What do you think the most important thing that affect our health?<br />5, Is it possible we can prolong our‘health life span’?<br /><br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Session 2: What steals my time?</span><br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://moneyminiblog.com/how-to/take-control-of-your-time/">https://moneyminiblog.com/how-to/take-c ... your-time/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1, Do you think you are a good time-manager?<br />2, What steals your time every day? What is the biggest thief?<br />3, What can you do with the time-thief?<br />4, What do think of the tips mentioned in the article?<br />5, To you personally, what is the most important thing you want to do at this stage of life?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=25437">Michael</a> — Sat Sep 05, 2020 10:32 pm</p><hr />
